name: Good Weed Home
description: Good Weed Home provides top-shelf and exotic marijuana strains, certified from our local and international growers and a wide range of cannabis products. We proudly invite you to the home of cannabis in Phuket, Thailand.

products_flowers.name: Persian Pie
products_flowers.description: The Persian Pie is our new combination of two powerful terpenes profiles. On one side the famous LemonTree from USA, known for its characteristical tree sap flavored with the most acid lemon profile, earthiness and citrus. And on the other side our powerful Banana Krumble, the sweetness and complexity of the banana flavor mixed with the power of the OG.

products_flowers.name: Full Gas
products_flowers.description: This cross is very special to the Green House Seeds family, because this cut of Exodus Cheese was selected with Dust when Franco was still living in Barcelona around 2015 and it has a special meaning to us. To pair this incredible strain that is the Exodus Cheese, which is so complex in taste already, we wanted to add something vigorous. We believe the best match for this, with gassy notes, (which is what we thought the exodus lacked), is one of our latest selections from Sunset Sherbert x Diagonal OG by Cannarado Genetics.

products_flowers.name: Lemon Orange
products_flowers.description: The Lemon Orange is the ideal strain for citrus lovers. The mix of our all-time champion, the Super Lemon Haze, with our own selection of Clementine from the Crockett family, which expresses some intense sweet clementine juice aromas without the acidity. Pure sweetness for the palate.

products_prerolls.name: Peanut butter
products_prerolls.description: Peanut Butter" and "Peanut Breath," is a hybrid marijuana strain known for its sedating effects. Crossed with Do-Si-Dos and Mendo Breath, Peanut Butter Breath has a unique nutty and earthy terpene profile when smoked. Beyond the terps, this strain will bring you down into a quality state of chill and relaxation. Originally from ThugPug Genetics, Peanut Butter Breath is very popular and there are many Do-Si-Dos and Mendo Breath crosses out there‚Äîbreeders Clout King have one called ‚ÄúPeanut Butter Cup.‚Äù

reviews.author: Georgy Volodin
reviews.content:
I have been to many weed places in Phuket. This one is a true gem. Good Weed Home is located in the beautiful semi rural/touristic place of Cape Panwa. The store offers you a great range of different edibles, sorts of cannabis and drinks (they say that soon they will start making food!).

But the main advantage is that the guys working here are absolutely awesome. They treat you not only as a customer but as a true friend. Very generous, fancy-looking guys and girls of Good Weed are always happy to consult and just talk on any topics. They play the best reggae/indie/blues folk tunes and invite local musicians to perform music live.

The atmosphere in this place is absolutely unique. I have not seen anything like this anywhere.

This place is unique, really.
